    <author>
      <name>Mend Release Bot</name>
    </author>
    <content type="html">&lt;p local-id="9aeb7365-192a-4caa-999f-0e46573bf0cd"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;New Features and Updates&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul local-id="339ad523-ceb7-467c-9ae6-dd73678d67cd"&gt;&lt;li local-id="a5e7eeea-a343-48b1-af69-1e3bbb866c34"&gt;&lt;p local-id="1084cd3f-b31e-497e-96df-f01d69b6aef6"&gt;Introducing a &lt;a data-linked-resource-id="3987767385" data-linked-resource-type="page" data-linked-resource-version="14" href="https://docs.mend.io/platform/latest/the-applications-and-projects-views"&gt;natural language search bar powered by AI&lt;/a&gt;, enabling users to filter applications and projects with intuitive prompts. This feature streamlines finding critical information, offers smart filter suggestions, and enhances the overall user experience with quick, relevant results and improved filter management.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li local-id="72fb0d3c-0a7c-48f5-b3e2-5e2c68d84c18"&gt;&lt;p local-id="862fec0e-394d-428f-abe9-7993e5522b33"&gt;Enhanced &lt;a data-linked-resource-id="2813526062" data-linked-resource-type="page" data-linked-resource-version="37" href="https://docs.mend.io/platform/latest/configure-single-sign-on-sso"&gt;SAML integration&lt;/a&gt; with new configuration options, improved user provisioning controls, and a modernized UI for a more flexible and secure authentication experience. Updates include, but are not limited to, the following enhancements: &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul local-id="57f2b242-fab8-4d30-a91b-f332a7fb2fe9"&gt;&lt;li local-id="45939bbb-2ec9-42c7-bf2c-871313e83be9"&gt;&lt;p local-id="ff5bcc74-bb6a-4e03-b0d8-1ab381bc9a0b"&gt;Disabling local logins &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li local-id="d7ce33d8-2f4a-4f62-a939-692c67513eeb"&gt;&lt;p local-id="d0aee82a-249e-4d17-8298-b7c3b8c84465"&gt;Toggling just-in-time user creation &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li local-id="27785571-413c-4811-a5f5-115cb1f250e1"&gt;&lt;p local-id="99c2e5fb-913f-4879-9c8e-c31493ca2ca8"&gt;Uploading or editing metadata in multiple formats &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li local-id="d2544fb2-bb23-4474-a8e8-494aec20c4cb"&gt;&lt;p local-id="069db085-4148-4a59-8bb3-3f84b6fc14ad"&gt;Notifications and visual indicators when the SAML certificate is close to expiration&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li local-id="6425d0ef-bb15-4707-95d3-fbd0c73a8724"&gt;&lt;p local-id="8c13b9d0-f946-4989-ab85-5148fca9bd4d"&gt;A two-way SSO enforcement across the Mend AppSec Platform and Legacy SCA application.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</content>
